Use the standard library

This is how to get_row of lst and x:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this lst's length times:
      Remember that row is item i in lst
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this row's length times:
         When item j in row is x, then:
            Add result to [i, j]
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know